All About Your Librarian

Hello! I am Mrs. Rupard, your school library media specialist.  Welcome to the library! I am so excited that you are here.  You will find lots of helpful resources on this page.  Please let me know if you need any help.

Vision Statement

Click to edit text

Our library's vision is to foster an environment of learning and literacy that empowers students with 21st century skills, incorporating critical thinking, collaboration, creativity, communication, and citizenship throughout the school, and beyond the community.

Mission Statement

Click to edit text

The mission of the school library is to provide a safe, inviting, learning environment that ensures the success of students and educators to be effective users of ideas, information, and technology empowering the learning community to be enthusiastic readers, lifelong learners, and critical thinkers.
